   [30 pts] Four friends, David, Susan, Tom and Carl, are going to the movies. Your program needs to provide seating instructions to them. The program should print:
   ::

     David will take the first seat
     Susan will sit next to David
     Tom will sit next to Susan
     Carl will sit next to Tom

   Below is some code to get you started:
   ~~~~
   prev= "David" 
   print(prev, "will take the first seat")
   for c in ["Susan", "Tom", "Carl"]: